---
title: Greek-Inspired Roasted Shrimp Dinner with Lemony Feta Sauce and Fresh Salad
description: This fresh seafood dinner is sure to please the whole family. Roasted shrimp gets the Greek treatment when paired with feta-dill sauce and brings balance and flavour to your dinner table any night of the week.

